full_text: Potential grand jurors in Georgia's Fulton County have been ordered to arrive at a courthouse Monday as part of a county prosecutor’s probe into alleged efforts by former President Donald Trump and others to overturn the state’s 2020 election results https://t.co/MYOL7doSxZ
